pproach based on the replacement of the producer's bid by a bid composed by\nthe regulator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jul 2015 08:28:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Aug 2021 08:29:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
